cas core
===============
attached is a cas core implementation in verilog. it implement 
a cas descrambler

reference:
		csa.c and csa.h in vlc opensource project.




Status
======
7-sep-2007	added key csa_ComputeKey

 
Directory Structure
===================
[core_root]
 |
 +-doc                        Documentation
 |
 +-bench--+                   Test Bench
 |
 +-rtl----+                   Core RTL Sources


